metadata.title: WOLVERINE Men's Kickstart DuraShocks 6 Inch Composite Toe Construction Boot
features: Shaft measures approximately Ankle" from arch

Premium nubuck leather upper Breathable moisture managing mesh lining Removable full-cushion footbed Advanced comfort lighweight PU midsole Wolverine DuraShocks dual suspension pad outsole Lightweight cement construction ASTM F2413-18 M I/75 C/75 rated composite safety toe
description: Step into comfort with Wolverine's latest DuraShocks product, the Kickstart. Wolverine DuraShocks technology features two pads at key strike points in the outsole to absorb shock and return energy to power you forward. With breathable nubuck leather uppers, the Kickstart is built to age well and only get more comfortable over time.
